title: Multi Agent Optimisation
author: Aditya Mahakali
description: This API provides multiple endpoints to generate, describe, and refine prompts for AI-based image generation using FastAPI. The main features include generating images based on user prompts, describing and scoring the generated images, and refining the prompts to improve the image output. The API also supports three major search strategies: **Beam Search**, **Best-First Search**, and **Breadth-First Search**.
